## Write a program to convert hours to seconds

1 hour = 60 minutes = 3600 seconds

```
Input  : 5
Output : 18000
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-hours-to-seconds" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main(){

    int n;
    scanf("%d",&n);
    printf("%d",n*3600);
    return 0;
}

//Contributed by Raghav Garg
```

```cpp
#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
    long double sec,hours;
